        "content": "<h3>The term cloud ecommerce refers to the process of outsourcing of a remote network of servers hosted on the Internet to use application services, store and process data. Cloud ecommerce solutions provide a wide range of benefits over traditional on-premise digital commerce solutions. Within the last ten years, cloud-based commerce has grown exponentially due to the efficiency of the cloud &ndash; cloud-based services save time and money.</h3>\n",
